const EN = require("./EN");

  normalEn : EN.normalEn,
  SolidBlock : EN.SolidBlock,
  BorderBlock : EN.BorderBlock,
  DotBlock : EN.DotBlock,
  GaintBold : EN.GaintBold,
  Btalic : EN.Btalic,
  GaintItalic : EN.GaintItalic,
